## Anti-Slop Rules (ALWAYS ACTIVE)

**BLOCK**:
- Inter as primary font
- blue-500/blue-600 as primary
- purple-to-pink gradient
- Generic empty states
- No micro-interactions

---

## Workflow

```
/brand     → Choose personality (6 options) → config/brand-identity.json
/build    → Build with brand values
/polish   → Quality pass
/test     → Verify
/preview  → Performance audit
```

